Subject: Secunia Research: Microsoft PowerPoint PP7X32.DLL
	Record Parsing Vulnerability

====================================================================== 

                     Secunia Research 09/11/2010

   - Microsoft PowerPoint PP7X32.DLL Record Parsing Vulnerability -

